{'dateCreated': <DateTime '20191212T15:53:00' at 0x1a4f2a19a08>, 'description': '全局监听enter键，是把监听事件绑定到document上\n常用的keyCode键盘编码在这里：https://www.cnblogs.com/wbyixx/p/12029508.html\n\n```js\ncreated: function() {\n        var _this = this;\n        document.onkeydown = function(e) {\n            let key = window.event.keyCode;\n            if (key == 13) {\n                _this.submit();\n            }\n        };\n    },\n```\n\n```js\nmethods: {\n        submit: function() {\n            alert("监听到enter键");\n        },\n   }\n```', 'title': 'Vue中全局监听键盘事件', 'categories': ['[随笔分类]FrontEnd~Vue', '[随笔分类]FrontEnd~Vue'], 'enclosure': {'length': 0}, 'link': 'https://www.cnblogs.com/wbyixx/p/12029684.html', 'permalink': 'https://www.cnblogs.com/wbyixx/p/12029684.html', 'postid': '12029684', 'source': {}, 'userid': '-2'}